358—84. Hexagonal Signs. The first hexagon comprises Aries, Gemini, Leo, Libra, Sagittarius, Aquarius; the second, Taurus, Cancer, Virgo, Scorpion, Capricorn, Pisces. Their position makes their influence weak; but they get some compensating advantage in that the members of each hexagon are all of one sex.
